Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.56,0:03:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\c&Hffffff&}♪～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.56,0:03:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}（只野）ひ… 瞳さん？
