Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.43,0:05:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}（片居）僕が師匠に勝ってるのは\N筋肉量ぐらいしか…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.39,0:05:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\c&Hffffff&}～♪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.90,0:05:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\c&Hffffff&}～♪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.90,0:05:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}よ… 喜んでくれたかな？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.40,0:05:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\c&Hffffff&}～♪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.90,0:05:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\c&Hffffff&}～♪
